data.description: This gorgeous home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and 1,499 sqft. of living space setting on 3 acres. The covered front porch is ideal for sitting and unwinding after a long day. There is a nice flow to this home with the living room transitioning into the dining area which is open to the kitchen with all these rooms having hardwood floors. The kitchen has a breakfast bar and plenty of cabinets and counter space. This primary bedroom is huge and has a walk-in closet and attached private bath that has a dual sink vanity and a tub/shower combo. The additional bedrooms have hardwood floors and share a full hall bathroom. There is a rear deck that leads out to the backyard with a storage shed and a generator that conveys. An attached 2-car garage is handy when coming in from wet weather. There is a new roof, tankless water heater, home recently painted and the heat pump is only 5 years old. The only thing missing from this home is you!
